      <title>巴西大豆利润因疲软货币交易而上涨，这对美国农民造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/brazil-soy-profits-fueled-by-weak-currency-in-blow-to-us-farmers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去一个月巴西货币的下跌，使这个世界最大大豆出口国的农民免受今年大豆价格暴跌的影响，使他们比美国竞争对手更具优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/brazil-soy-profits-fueled-by-weak-currency-in-blow-to-us-farmers</guid>
