      <title>制药公司 DRI 因首席执行官因费用调查离职而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/pharma-company-dri-plunges-as-ceo-leaves-cfo-suspended-in-expenses-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在其首席执行官因费用问题接受审查后离职后，DRI Healthcare Trust 股价一度下跌 32%，为该公司上市三年多以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/pharma-company-dri-plunges-as-ceo-leaves-cfo-suspended-in-expenses-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 17:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
